&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Geetanjali
&lt;div id="geetanjali" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#geetanjali" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>यत्र मनः भयरहितमस्ति शिरः च उन्नतमस्ति&lt;br>
यत्र ज्ञानम् मुक्तम् प्रवहति&lt;br>
यत्र सङ्कीर्ण-प्राकारैह् सम्सारः भग्नः न अभवत्&lt;br>
यत्र पदानि ह्इदयगाम्भिर्यतः आगच्छति&lt;br>
यत्र श्रान्तरहितॊद्यमम् पूर्णतॊन्मुखमस्ति&lt;br>
यत्र बुधिधारायाः मार्गभ्रम्शम् निर्जन-मरुभुम्याम् न अभवत्&lt;br>
यत्र मनः भवता प्रकर्ष्यते विशालचिन्तनाय कर्माय च&lt;br>
मुक्तेह् तत्-स्वर्गार्थम् मम राष्ट्रमुधरॆत्&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Important Samskrut Sloka</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/important-samskrut-sloka/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/important-samskrut-sloka/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/SanskritYatra-Sloka.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">Important Samskrut Sloka
&lt;div id="important-samskrut-sloka" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#important-samskrut-sloka" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>To remember list of 10 cardinal Upnishad&lt;/p>
&lt;p>ईशकेनकठप्रश्नमुण्डमाण्डूक्यतित्तिरि ।&lt;br>
एतरेयं च छान्दोग्यं बृहदारण्यकं तथा ।।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>1-ईश 2-केन 3-कठ 4-प्रश्न 5-मुण्ड 6-माण्डूक्य 7-तित्तिरि 8-एतरेय 9-छान्दोग्य 10-बृहदारण्यक&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To remember list of all Purana&lt;/p>
&lt;p>मद्वयं भद्वयं चैव ब्रत्रयं वचतुष्टयम् ।&lt;br>
अ ना प लिं ग कू स्का नि पुराणानि प्रचक्षते ।।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>1- Matsya-Markandeya, 3- Bhagwat-Bhavishya, 5- Brahmand-Brahma-Brahmavaivart, 8- Vishnu-Vaman-Vayu-Varaha, 12-Agni, 13-Narayana, 14-Padma, 15-Linga, 16-Garduda, 17-Kurma, 18-Skanda&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Sanskrit Subhashitam - संस्कृत सुभाषितम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/sanskrit-subhashitas-1/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/sanskrit-subhashitas-1/</guid><description>&lt;p>
